data.description: AMAZING LOCATED HOME in the suburbs off TAMPA!! 3 bed / 2 bath home, WITH 2 BALCONIES, OVERSIZED SIDE-ENTRY 2-CAR GARAGE, OVERSIZED LOT, NEWER ROOF AND HVAC, and water softener.  NO HOA!!  Walking into the home, you'll find a beautiful entry with GORGEOUS vinyl tile flooring, wrap-staircase with rot-iron balusters, and shiplap accent wall.  The living room is large enough to accommodate a sectional couch plus bonus space.  The kitchen was remodeled in 2018 with Quartz countertops and new cabinets.  The stainless-steel appliances are even newer.  There is a spot for barstools off the kitchen leading into the healthy sized dining room.  All Bedrooms are up-stairs with PRIVATE BALCONIES on Master & 2 Bedroom. Master Bedroom includes walk in closet, Master bath has dual sinks with Shower & Tub. Bedroom 2 & 3 share a bathroom with a Tub & Shower. Nearly fully fenced large backyard with plenty of room to play and leading to a retention pond! Centrally located to US 41, I275 & all local Parks, venues, shopping, restaurants, hospitals, etc... Less than 30 Minutes from downtown Tampa & Curtis Hixon Park and 2 of TOP 10 BEACHES IN THE COUNTRY (St Petersburgh and Clearwater).
